<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 03:12:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>独家：渣打银行暂停客户通过中国境外渠道进行新投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/stanchart-suspends-new-investments-clients-via-chinas-outbound-channel-2024-02-27/</link><description>专注于亚洲的渣打银行在给路透社的一份声明中表示，自上周以来，渣打银行已暂停其中国客户通过基于配额的渠道购买新的离岸产品。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 02:21:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/stanchart-suspends-new-investments-clients-via-chinas-outbound-channel-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>日本股市飙升让投资者远离陷入困境的中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/soaring-japanese-equities-offer-investors-cozy-distance-troubled-china-2024-02-27/</link><description>随着经济和地缘政治困境促使投资者大量逃离中国，许多人将资金转向日本，这给基准日经指数带来了额外的提振，使其飙升至历史新高。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 02:04:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/soaring-japanese-equities-offer-investors-cozy-distance-troubled-china-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>日本通胀高于预期，亚洲股市动荡，交易员保持警惕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-27/</link><description>亚洲股市周二艰难上涨，日本通胀略高于预期，令投资者在本周欧洲和美国公布价格数据之前保持警惕。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 01:59:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>台湾称5艘中国海警船进入前线岛屿附近海域</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-minister-says-5-china-coast-guard-ships-entered-waters-around-kinmen-2024-02-27/</link><description>台湾一位部长周二表示，在与北京的紧张关系持续升级之际，五艘中国海警船周一进入台湾前线金门岛周围的禁区或限制水域，但在被警告离开后不久就离开了。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 01:23:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-minister-says-5-china-coast-guard-ships-entered-waters-around-kinmen-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>随着美国关键数据的临近，美元下跌；日元因 CPI 上涨而走强</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-droops-key-us-data-looms-yen-firms-cpi-beat-2024-02-27/</link><description>周二美元走势不利，因为市场期待一周的美国关键经济数据，这些数据将提供有关美联储可能多久开始降息的新信号。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 01:20:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-droops-key-us-data-looms-yen-firms-cpi-beat-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>夏威夷邻国基里巴斯发现中国警察后美国发出警告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-cautions-after-hawaii-neighbor-kiribati-gets-chinese-police-2024-02-27/</link><description>在路透社报道中国警察正在夏威夷邻国基里巴斯偏远环礁国家工作后，美国周一警告太平洋岛国不要接受中国安全部队的援助。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 01:19:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-cautions-after-hawaii-neighbor-kiribati-gets-chinese-police-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国房地产危机刺激需求，重组专家增加香港员工</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/restructuring-specialists-boost-hong-kong-staff-china-property-crisis-stokes-2024-02-26/</link><description>随着中国的房地产危机导致债务重组交易激增，全球重组专家 Alvarez &amp;amp; Marsal 和 Houlihan Lokey 增加了在香港的员工数量，使其成为香港金融业招聘中罕见的亮点。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 23:28:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/restructuring-specialists-boost-hong-kong-staff-china-property-crisis-stokes-2024-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>巴西BRF结束七连败，扭亏为盈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brazils-brf-ends-seven-quarter-losing-streak-earns-16526-million-q4-2024-02-26/</link><description>根据周一的财报，巴西家禽和猪肉加工商 BRF SA 在 2023 年最后三个月实现利润 8.23 亿雷亚尔（1.6526 亿美元），结束了连续七个季度的亏损。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 23:02:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brazils-brf-ends-seven-quarter-losing-streak-earns-16526-million-q4-2024-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>美国参议院委员会就中国药明康德和华大基因法案举行听证会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/us-senate-panel-sets-hearing-chinas-wuxi-apptec-bgi-bill-2024-02-26/</link><description>美国参议院一个委员会周一表示，将于 3 月 6 日就一项禁止联邦机构与中国华大基因、药明康德和其他受关注生物技术公司签订合同的法案举行听证会。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 22:59:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/us-senate-panel-sets-hearing-chinas-wuxi-apptec-bgi-bill-2024-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>美国称中国航空公司可将美国航班增加至每周 50 班</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinese-passenger-airlines-can-increase-number-us-flights-usdot-2024-02-26/</link><description>美国运输部周一表示，从 3 月 31 日起，中国客运航空公司将被允许将每周往返美国的航班从目前的 35 班增加到 50 班，从而使市场恢复到大流行前水平的近三分之一。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 22:23:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinese-passenger-airlines-can-increase-number-us-flights-usdot-2024-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>古巴顶级雪茄制造商因高端需求蓬勃发展而创下销售纪录</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/cubas-top-cigar-maker-smokes-sales-record-booming-high-end-demand-2024-02-26/</link><description>古巴顶级雪茄制造商哈伯纳斯周一表示，其2023年销售额已飙升至创纪录的7.21亿美元，该公司高管将这一基准归因于中国等市场对其最豪华、高端雪茄的需求旺盛。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 22:16:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/cubas-top-cigar-maker-smokes-sales-record-booming-high-end-demand-2024-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：日本两年来首次通胀低于预期？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-02-26/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 21:46:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>国际原子能机构文件称，伊朗浓缩铀库存减少至60%，但问题依然存在</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/irans-uranium-stock-enriched-60-shrinks-problems-persist-iaea-papers-say-2024-02-26/</link><description>联合国核监督机构周一的报告称，伊朗的接近武器级的浓缩铀库存已经减少，使其低于可以生产三颗原子弹的理论阈值，但检查人员的问题仍然存在。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 18:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/irans-uranium-stock-enriched-60-shrinks-problems-persist-iaea-papers-say-2024-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>独家：财政部称美国对银行的警告减缓了俄罗斯的资金流动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/treasury-says-us-warning-banks-slows-russia-financial-flows-2024-02-26/</link><description>美国财政部副部长沃利·阿德耶莫表示，华盛顿威胁对外国金融机构实施制裁，这对俄罗斯与土耳其、阿拉伯联合酋长国和哈萨克斯坦等国之间的资金流动产生了重大影响。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 17:34:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/treasury-says-us-warning-banks-slows-russia-financial-flows-2024-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>发言人称美国商会会长本周将访华</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-chamber-commerce-chief-visiting-china-this-week-spokesperson-says-2024-02-26/</link><description>该组织表示，美国商会首席执行官苏珊·克拉克本周将率领一个由前美国政府官员组成的代表团访问北京。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 17:22:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-chamber-commerce-chief-visiting-china-this-week-spokesperson-says-2024-02-26/</guid></item></channel></rss>